               <code code="51727-6" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="INACTIVE INGREDIENT SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Inactive Ingredients: Carbomer, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cypress Oil, Glyceryl
Stearate, Green 3 (CI# 42053), Hypromellose, Isopropyl Palmitate,
Methylisothiazolinone, Phenoxyethanol, Polysorbate-60, Propylene
Glycol, Sodium Hydroxide, Stearyl Alcohol, Water.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20120818"/>
            </section>
         </component>
